{"tid":1780211,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［原本應該告酷刑罪］涉虐待被捕長者　三警改控公職人員行為失當罪","createTime":"2019-12-12T07:54:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-12T08:10:43.000Z","uid":22556,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8f9e2b5e4abdc291bd01e3550d2719000b8fc0f9","tid":1780211,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T07:54:13.000Z","msg":"名現仼及已離職警員涉於今年 6 月底在北區醫院內虐打62歲男子，被控襲擊致造成身體傷害罪及串謀作上述罪行，案件今於沙田裁判法院再提堂，控方申請將控罪改為公職人員行為失當及襲擊致造成身體傷害罪，後者為前者的交替控罪，三人暫毋須答辯，案件押後至明年1月7日再訊，以便控方準備轉介文件，將案件轉介區域法院處理，期間三人獲准繼續保釋。控方表示，已多次向醫管局及社署要求索取事主的醫療及創傷報告，但仍無法獲取相關報告。<br />\n<br />\n首兩名被告為現職警員的歐國偉（25 歲）及鄧文謙（24 歲），兩人均隸屬上水分區，原被控襲擊致造成身體傷害罪。第三位被告則為已離職警員林易昇（30歲），原被控串謀襲擊致造成身體傷害罪。<br />\n<br />\n控方今修訂控罪，改控三名被告公職人員行為失當罪，指三人今年 6 月 26 日在上水北區醫院，身為警務人員無合理辯解而故意作出不當行為，即襲擊被羈押中的男子鍾志華。交替的襲擊致造成身體傷害，指三人於同日同地襲擊男子鍾志華。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B6%89%E8%99%90%E5%BE%85%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%E9%95%B7%E8%80%85-%E4%B8%89%E8%AD%A6%E6%94%B9%E6%8E%A7%E5%85%AC%E8%81%B7%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E8%A1%8C%E7%82%BA%E5%A4%B1%E7%95%B6%E7%BD%AA-%E8%BD%89%E4%BB%8B%E5%8D%80%E9%99%A2%E8%99%95%E7%90%86/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B6%2589%25E8%2599%2590%25E5%25BE%2585%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595%25E9%2595%25B7%25E8%2580%2585-%25E4%25B8%2589%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2594%25B9%25E6%258E%25A7%25E5%2585%25AC%25E8%2581%25B7%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%25A1%258C%25E7%2582%25BA%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E7%2595%25B6%25E7%25BD%25AA-%25E8%25BD%2589%25E4%25BB%258B%25E5%258D%2580%25E9%2599%25A2%25E8%2599%2595%25E7%2590%2586%2F&d=Vh0AUGqI%2BhuKY3uG7C8Fc4T2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=9f67aa30\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B6%2589%25E8%2599%2590%25E5%25BE%2585%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595%25E9%2595%25B7%25E8%2580%2585-%25E4%25B8%2589%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2594%25B9%25E6%258E%25A7%25E5%2585%25AC%25E8%2581%25B7%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%25A1%258C%25E7%2582%25BA%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E7%2595%25B6%25E7%25BD%25AA-%25E8%25BD%2589%25E4%25BB%258B%25E5%258D%2580%25E9%2599%25A2%25E8%2599%2595%25E7%2590%2586%2F&h=05b0c183\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B6%89%E8%99%90%E5%BE%85%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%E9%95%B7%E8%80%85-%E4%B8%89%E8%AD%A6%E6%94%B9%E6%8E%A7%E5%85%AC%E8%81%B7%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E8%A1%8C%E7%82%BA%E5%A4%B1%E7%95%B6%E7%BD%AA-%E8%BD%89%E4%BB%8B%E5%8D%80%E9%99%A2%E8%99%95%E7%90%86/</a>"},{"pid":"51001f6d31ee755b35584d1e10981c5d0a0e4144","tid":1780211,"uid":75311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T07:58:23.000Z","msg":"殺人 放火 金腰帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e630540f1a77a10fa652ec2f6a4c6569e8a67184","tid":1780211,"uid":251083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T08:00:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dff71170ff00172c415dccab17c780b62eae43c4","tid":1780211,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T08:10:43.000Z","msg":"唔關政治事都要攬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,藍絲醒未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}